Package: HandyCNV
Type: Package
Title: HandyCNV: An R package for Standardized Summary, Annotation, Comparison, and Visualization of CNV, CNVR and ROH 
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Jinghang Zhou, Liyuan Liu, Yuangang Shi, Dorian Garrick
Maintainer: JH Zhou <zjhang027@gmail.com>
Description: The package is aimed to provide a Standard, Reproducible and Time-saving pipelines for the post-analysis of CNV and CNVR.
